Description: Lug Womens Puddle Jumper Overnight 2.0 Gym Bag, Spice Orange, One Size Description Top choice for the true traveler. Thought-of-everything touches include a handy removable pouch, hidden magnetic pocket, and detachable mirror. Not too big and not too small, with a pocket or pouch for every last thing, it's easy to see why this bag is a best seller. Or the ventilated compartment that keeps the dirty clothes/shoes away from the clean. Or the - you get the picture. This bag has all the bells and whistles.
